response.overview: After the unexpected death of the Pope, Cardinal Lawrence is tasked with managing the covert and ancient ritual of electing a new one. Sequestered in the Vatican with the Catholic Church’s most powerful leaders until the process is complete, Lawrence finds himself at the center of a conspiracy that could lead to its downfall.
response.tagline: What happens behind these walls will change everything.
response.title: Conclave

release_dates.note: Mar Del Plata International Film Festival
